    <div class="main review-item" id="7868884">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7868884/" class="title-link">通俗历史解读战国风云</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7868884"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/144888125/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/144888125/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">极恶魔王</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-04-26"
      class="main-meta">2016-04-26 19:12:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7868884_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看这本书前，网上有人说不要读袁腾飞的书。大体意思是说，现在冠以通俗、幽默等标签的历史书，往往很浅薄，而且加入了作者大量的主观观念和说教性文字，往往灌输于人一些所谓的宏大的意义。仔细想想，这种问题很好理解，本人基于对于战国那段历史的喜好开启了这本书的阅读，对...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
